{
  "texts": [
    "The authors create their dataset, using a LIDAR or a timeof-flight (ToF) camera to scan buildings and create point clouds (Ma et al. 2020a).",
    "Furthermore, they modified the scans (Liu et al. 2018) to be incomplete.",
    "However, the VSL network is pretrained on the ModelNet (Wu et al. 2015) synthetic dataset.",
    "However, limitations for this approach exist.",
    "The lack of automated change detection, limited resolution, and diversity necessitates more real-life data."
  ]
}